stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> UNKNOWN : Server startup

    UNKNOWN --> CONNECTED : First message received

    CONNECTED --> DEGRADED : Silence > 30s\nOR gap rate > 0.1%
    CONNECTED --> RECONNECTING : TCP disconnect

    DEGRADED --> CONNECTED : Message received,\ngap rate normalised
    DEGRADED --> RECONNECTING : Silence > 120s

    RECONNECTING --> CONNECTED : Reconnection successful
    RECONNECTING --> FALLBACK_ACTIVE : Attempts > 3

    FALLBACK_ACTIVE --> CONNECTED : DataBento reconnected

    CONNECTED --> OFFLINE : Manual shutdown\nOR unrecoverable error
    DEGRADED --> OFFLINE : Manual shutdown
    RECONNECTING --> OFFLINE : Manual shutdown
    FALLBACK_ACTIVE --> OFFLINE : Manual shutdown

    note right of CONNECTED
        M-16 in watchdog mode
        DataBento triggers processBar()
        Parity monitor active
    end note

    note right of FALLBACK_ACTIVE
        M-16 triggers processBar()
        DataBento bars stored but not used
        Owner notified
    end note

    note right of RECONNECTING
        Exponential backoff: 1s, 2s, 4s, 8s, 16s, 32s, 60s max
        M-16 continues as primary
        Dashboard shows RECONNECTING
    end note
